## Anti-Patterns (What Bad Looks Like)

### "AI Slop" Aesthetic
- Multiple font weights competing (300, 400, 500, 600, 700 all visible)
- Purple/blue gradients on white
- Generic stock photography
- Every element has different visual treatment
- No clear point of view
- Inter font everywhere

### "Template Site" Feel
- Obvious grid with no variation
- Every section looks the same
- Buttons that all look different from each other
- Mixed icon styles
- Inconsistent spacing
- Corporate blue CTAs

### Visual Noise
- Too many colors
- Too many boxes/borders
- Icons everywhere
- Text in all caps mixed with sentence case
- Competing visual elements

